<section class="grid-container" id="index-card1">
    <div>
        <article class="subtitle">
            <h2>The Rhinoceros</h2>
        </article>
        <article class="body">
            <p><span>Status: Critically Endangered</span></p>
            <p>Populations of rhino declined dramatically in the 20th century at the hands of European hunters and
                settlers
                to less than 2,500. Thanks to persistent conservation efforts across Africa, rhino numbers have doubled
                from
                their historic low 20 years ago to between 5,042 and 5,455 today.</p>
            <p>However, the rhino is still considered critically endangered, and a lot of work remains to bring the
                numbers
                up to even a fraction of what it once was—and to ensure that it stays there.</p>
        </article>
    </div>
</section>

